title: Most shazamed songs of all time worldwide 2018
summary: This is a bar chart representing Song Titles in the x axis and Number of identifications in millions in the y axis.
The Number of identifications in millions is appeared to be the highest at Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii and lowest at Song Titles All of Me by John Legend.
There is a difference of 6.19 between the maximum Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii and minimum Song Titles All of Me by John Legend.

max_summary: This bar chart has 10 columns on the x axis representing Song Titles, and Number of identifications in millions in each Song Titles on the y axis.
The Number of identifications in millions is highest at Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii and lowest at Song Titles All of Me by John Legend.
Song Titles Somebody That I Used To Know by Gotye feat. Kimbra has the second highest value for Number of identifications in millions.
There is a difference of 6.19 between the maximum Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii and minimum Song Titles All of Me by John Legend.

Number of identifications in millions at Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii is 23.77 , second place is Somebody That I Used To Know by Gotye feat. Kimbra at 21.63, and thirdly is Lean On by Major Lazer Feat. MØ & DJ Snake at 21.38.
The Song Titles All of Me by John Legend tends to be 1.15 percent lower than average.
Summing up the values of all Song Titless, we get total 206.43.
